  "description": "<h3>Product Specifications Table</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Product Number</th><th>Specification</th><th>Product Size (L\u00d7W\u00d7H) (inch)</th><th>Package Size (L\u00d7W\u00d7H) (inch)</th><th>Product Weight (lb)</th><th>Package Weight (lb)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>ZHUMI-CJ-WH01-F</td><td>FULL</td><td>74.40 x 53.50 x 12.00</td><td>75.70 x 10.60 x 7.40</td><td>50.40</td><td>55.30</td></tr><tr><td>ZHUMI-CJ-WH01-T</td><td>TWIN</td><td>74.40 x 37.90 x 12.00</td><td>75.70 x 9.40 x 7.40</td><td>34.60</td><td>40.30</td></tr><tr><td>ZHUMI-CJ-WH01-Q</td><td>QUEEN</td><td>79.50 x 59.40 x 12.00</td><td>80.70 x 10.60 x 7.40</td><td>54.10</td><td>60.40</td></tr><tr><td>ZHUMI-CJ-WH01-K</td><td>KING</td><td>79.50 x 75.50 x 12.00</td><td>88.50 x 10.60 x 7.40</td><td>58.60</td><td>66.60</td></tr></tbody></table>\n <p><br/>Description:</p>\n <ul>\n  <li>STURDY AND DURABLE: The wooden bed frame comes with wooden slats made of durable solid wood and is designed for long term use. With a weight capacity of up to 1000lbs, it offers more support than other similar products!</li>\n  <li>NO HEADBOARD DESIGN: This wooden bed frame is a perfect blend of minimalist and modern style. The headboard-less design allows for more space in the room. Creates a comfortable and cosy space for rest and relaxation.</li>\n  <li>NO SPRINGS REQUIRED: The sturdy, closely spaced wooden slats of this bed frame support all types of mattresses, prolonging their life without the need for springs.</li>\n  <li>SPACE SAVING: There is 8.5 inches of space underneath the bed frame to store items. Meet your diverse storage solutions and keep your room neat and orderly.</li>\n  <li>EASY INSTALLATION: Simply follow the instructions and videos. All accessories are included to save you installation time.</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/f5acea41-9eca-4b00-b158-7af196956d04.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/4f99f3